name: Laws of Karma — #10 Law of Change
description:
Have you ever feel like going nowhere? If so, then maybe it's time for you to change. Your past will always repeat by itself, so the only way out of that cycle is by changing your direction.

Just like this snake, he was tired of slithering by his stomach. One day, he decided to grow up some legs and walk. He couldn't decide which one is better, but for him at least he was experiencing something new and it was exciting!
